  "text": "The inhibition kinetics of GSP on α-glucosidase was determined by preparing a series of sample solutions with various concentrations of substrate and GSP. The mode of inhibition of GSP was deduced from a Lineweaver-Burk plot and computed the Km (dissociation constant) and V max (maximum reaction velocity) of the enzyme [CITATION_1] .",
